      <odd id="aspace_e5fd2549621b155f2fbb70f505041c26">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 14-B (YRG 14-B), Records of academic departments and programs of the Yale Faculty of Arts and Sciences.</p>  
      </odd>
      <acqinfo id="aspace_2872eabd73703b9f31cae901aee711bd">
         <head>Immediate Source of Acquisition</head>
         <p>The records were transferred from the Department of Music, 2006.</p>  
      </acqinfo>
