      </prefercite>
      <arrangement id="aspace_ddb783cb4763369cf0a2ea4c8125d1be">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>The records are arranged by topic.</p>  
      </arrangement>
      <bioghist id="aspace_ec715789a5fe37a987d0ccb5a1507f68">
         <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
         <p>The Department of Music in Yale College offers undergraduate level courses in music history, theory, composition, and performance.</p>  
      </bioghist>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_43a07b77db35cd9e472ddf4e5bca231f">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of the files of the director of undergraduate studies, including correspondence, course files, syllabi, senior essays, grades, and financial records of the Yale Department of Music.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
